{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-jsx","path":"/blog/visuales-lupear/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Improvisaciones en el Espacio Latente — <a href=\"https://audiostellar.xyz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AudioStellar</a></h1>\n<p>Improvisaciones en el Espacio Latente es un periplo audiovisual inspirado en una deriva por los pliegues de la inteligencia artificial y sus espacios latentes dentro del microcosmos de AudioStellar, se recorre un paisaje espacial en búsqueda de posibles salidas.</p>\n<br>\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/kZhcpq4R4c0?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<br>\n<p>Visuales: Santiago Fernandez y Ramiro Arsanto.<br>\nSonido: Leandro Garber, Dai Miauro, Luca Belloti.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>16/10/22 Laboratorio de Artes Electrónicas, Tecnópolis</p>\n<div class=\"galeria\">\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a27b662a78cf99b3677b96c89063350e/0f98f/ast-luperar1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.29629629629629%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"AudioStellar Lupear\"\n        title=\"\"\n        